{"tid":1550283,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［全部同我入晒尼］每日十點唱國歌加鳩叫！","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T18:45:17.000Z","uid":69419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"03d9872df07e4e80e0d58bffbb419a8973af01f4","tid":1550283,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"每日十點除咗鳩叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地重可以練國歌㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ho9ajom.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHo9ajom.jpg&h=18f678bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC4c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=4f1cf52f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<code>希望有一日，十點一到，就有\n「何以 這土地 淚再流」</code>"},{"pid":"024dab041bb2dd73277d9cf985fbbd81eaea7945","tid":1550283,"uid":131122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:23:44.000Z","msg":"《洛杉磯時報》報道林鄭撤回修例時，有寫到大家轉載《凜冬烈火》的截圖：「If we accepted the government&rsquo;s conditions, our friends who&rsquo;ve already died would not forgive us.」證明大家的表態係非常重要，千萬不要小看自己。報道亦肯定了五大訴求缺一不可，證明美方不會單憑林鄭耍小動作，而放棄對香港的關注和對港共的制裁。<br />\n<br />\n至為緊要是最尾那一段預告：<br />\n<br />\nProtesters have called for a demonstration at the U.S. consulate Saturday to support the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act, a proposed bill that would strengthen U.S. backing for democratization and human rights in Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\n美方現正觀察林鄭電視講話後香港人的反應，如果我們在星期日的示威不夠熱烈，勢必予人一個錯誤的觀感，以為民情冷卻。所以我懇請大家，不只網上表態，也要用腳表態，在美國駐港領事館前，堅定促請美國國會通過《香港民主及人權法》。"},{"pid":"f082b335577898ca108977c1223d34649e4c9a90","tid":1550283,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"051b0b0547f1431a5cee097a0ffa198d61fef501","tid":1550283,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:58:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c536ada2e7e05810bcad1d62615e06cfe754cf7b","tid":1550283,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:02:57.000Z","msg":"自推10次<br />\npush"},{"pid":"b5924d9a53f22fe74d6b152af9ac544e65975e59","tid":1550283,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:03:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"932fa8c3c4ed10a84da549c58a445effc2a68ebd","tid":1550283,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:03:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f3e6a0b230c75c765d21cf0e10bf2efdad3a7a69","tid":1550283,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:03:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96aada5bc98278e91d8edf2594541019cd80fb8f","tid":1550283,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:03:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"021ed575c591763af8b8624028eba1d7df7d9bea","tid":1550283,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:04:02.0